SDLC : Agile 


Agile Way of Working 

Rituals :

1. Sprint Planning  : 2-Week Sprint : Tuesday - Tuesday - 1 Week & Tuesday - Tuesday -2 

2. Daily Standup  : Every Day i.e. Monday to Friday : 15minutes

3. Review		  : 3rd or 4th day of the week or only once in a sprint sprint : 30 or 60 minutes

4. Refinement     : During the sprint - we have to refine current sprint iteams or Product Backlogs

5. End the Sprint (Review, Demo & End Sprint & Start a New Sprint) : 

